===============
Getting Started
===============

1. Install Scala and SBT

2. In the directory where you would like to start your project, start up SBT

3. At the SBT prompt, create a scails project:

> scail myApp

Where "myApp" is the name of the application.

4. To see your application running, start the local Jetty server:

> jetty-run

Then visit http://localhost:8080

5. As features are developed, documentation will be created


